They say "our hands will burn, we can't". They want comfort.

126
00:26:05,000 --> 00:26:09,000
Lê dema nan tê pêşiya wan, dixwin?
 
But when the bread comes before them, do they eat?

127
00:26:09,000 --> 00:26:18,000
